logging.basicConfig(level=logging.DEBUG)
logging.debug("Debug message")


Used in:

Large projects

Production debugging

6Ô∏è‚É£ IDE Debugger (VS Code / PyCharm)

Set breakpoints

Step through code

Watch variable values

7Ô∏è‚É£ Unit Testing
python -m unittest


Used to:

Find bugs early

Validate logic

8Ô∏è‚É£ Check Inputs
print(type(value))


Used to:

Confirm correct data type

Avoid logical errors

9Ô∏è‚É£ Simplify Code

Break large code into small parts

Debug each part separately

One-Line Summary üß†

Python debugging = print + traceback + debugger + logging

